ZH: 演播室是一个专门用于电视或广播节目制作的地方。
EN: A studio is a place specifically designed for the production of television or radio programs.

ZH: 他们正在演播室中准备一个新的节目。
EN: They are preparing a new show in the studio.

ZH: 请不要在演播室内大声喧哗。
EN: Please refrain from making loud noises inside the studio.

ZH: 演播室里面有很多灯光和摄影设备。
EN: There are many lights and camera equipment in the studio.

ZH: 这个演播室由一支专业的制作团队负责。
EN: This studio is managed by a professional production team.

ZH: 每天都有不同的节目在这个演播室中录制。
EN: Different shows are recorded in this studio every day.

ZH: 我们需要去演播室进行一次采访。
EN: We need to go to the studio for an interview.

ZH: 她是这个演播室的主持人之一。
EN: She is one of the hosts in this studio.

ZH: 演播室提供了最新的音频和视频处理设备。
EN: The studio provides the latest audio and video processing equipment.

ZH: 这个演播室的声音效果非常好。
EN: The sound quality in this studio is excellent.

ZH: 演播室中有一个专门的化妆间供演员化妆。
EN: There is a dedicated dressing room in the studio for actors to do their makeup.

ZH: 我孩子在这个演播室上了一个音乐节目。
EN: My child performed a music program in this studio.

ZH: 这个演播室有一个巨大的绿幕，可用于特效合成。
EN: This studio has a large green screen that can be used for special effects.

ZH: 演播室的观众席可以容纳一百人。
EN: The audience seats in the studio can accommodate a hundred people.

ZH: 演播室的空调系统非常给力。
EN: The air conditioning system in the studio is very powerful.

ZH: 演播室里面有一个专门的控制室用于调控节目。
EN: There is a dedicated control room inside the studio for program regulation.

ZH: 我的朋友在这个演播室做摄影师。
EN: My friend works as a photographer in this studio.

ZH: 最近，这个演播室进行了一次全面的装修。
EN: Recently, this studio underwent a comprehensive renovation.

ZH: 这个演播室的装饰很时尚。
EN: The decoration of this studio is very trendy.

ZH: 这个演播室的工作人员非常友好和专业。
EN: The staff of this studio is very friendly and professional.
